27. Winter's Grasp - Channeled: 30 dmg/s + root
28. Ice Colossus - Summon ice guardian 300s

**Circle 8 (Mana: 80):**
29. Ice Age - AoE 20-tile: 100-150 dmg + permafreeze terrain
30. Avatar of Frost - Transform: +50 INT, +100% cold dmg 180s
